      "text": "ソラニン・チャンス",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed52",
      "text": "from [2026/04/08]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed53",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640672
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed54",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed55",
      "text": " マクドのポテトに緑のが入ってて報告するか迷っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed56",
      "text": "  滅多にない[ソラニン]を食べるチャンス",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed57",
      "text": "  食った(バカヤロウ)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed58",
      "text": "  コーヒーのせいで不味さが分からない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed59",
      "text": "  コレで体調を壊したら相当危ない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed5a",
      "text": "   今回は知ってて食べてるけど、知らずに食べても毒は毒なので、そういう事が起こり得るという事",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed5b",
      "text": "  量を調べると大分余裕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed5c",
      "text": "   見た目のキショさの割に余裕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e71b0000000000d4ed5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640667,
      "updated": 1778640667
    }
  ]
}